title: Folio Weekly (8-14 April 2015)

Folio Weekly (8-14 April 2015)
 English | PDF | 39 pages | 14 MB


Folio Weekly is an ultra-liberal free alternative weekly newspaper published in Jacksonville, Florida. Founded in 1987, it calls itself the largest and most influential alternative paper in Northeast Florida. It is a member of the Association of Alternative Newsmedia and has won three AAN Awards. The paper has an unknown circulation as it is free.[1]
